Namespace List
Here is a list of all namespaces with brief descriptions:
[detail level 123]
Tag
TagLibA namespace for all TagLib related classes and functions
APEAn implementation of APE metadata
ASFAn implementation of ASF (WMA) metadata
FLACAn implementation of FLAC metadata
ID3v1An ID3v1 implementation
ID3v2An ID3v2 implementation
SynchDataA few functions for ID3v2 synch safe integer conversion
MP4An implementation of MP4 (AAC, ALAC, ...) metadata
MPCAn implementation of MPC metadata
MPEGAn implementation of TagLib::File with MPEG (MP3) specific methods
OggA namespace for the classes used by Ogg-based metadata files
FLACAn implementation of Ogg FLAC metadata
SpeexA namespace containing classes for Speex metadata
VorbisA namespace containing classes for Vorbis metadata
RIFFAn implementation of TagLib::File with RIFF specific methods
AIFFAn implementation of AIFF metadata
WAVAn implementation of WAV metadata
TrueAudioAn implementation of TrueAudio metadata
WavPackAn implementation of WavPack metadata
